Popular YouTube show Podcast and Chill with MacG will be heading to Pretoria at the SunBet Arena in April for their one million subscribers event. Podcaster and host of the show, Macgyver ‘MacG’ Mukwevho took to social media to announce the news of filling up the Arena on 15 April 2023. He shared a video of the podcast’s journey from the beginning to some of the iconic moments of the show. The event will feature a live recording of the podcast, as well as performances by some of Mzansi’s top entertainers. Fans will have the opportunity to interact with MacG and the team. “For the chillers who have been there since day one and even the ones who recently joined the movement, this one is for you,” he wrote.  For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here